title: NFL ATL: 2014 QB rankings
itunes:title: NFL ATL: 2014 QB rankings
description:
A room full of heroes -- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal, Chris Wesseling and Marc Sessler -- react to the latest NFL news including the Bills' Kiki Alonso's season-ending injury, Jimmy Graham's tight end ruling and more. The fantastic four also compare and contrast Wesseling's quarterback rankings' list with that of NFL coaches and executives. Lastly, find out which power running back is "Making the Leap".
